1178static uint16_T look1_iu16lu64n48_binlcse(uint16_T u0, const uint16_T bp0[],



1179  const uint16_T table[], uint32_T maxIndex)



1180{



1181  uint16_T y;



1182  uint64_T frac;



1183  uint32_T iRght;



1184  uint32_T iLeft;



1185  uint32_T bpIdx;



1186



1187  /* Lookup 1-D



1188     Search method: 'binary'



1189     Use previous index: 'off'



1190     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



1191     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



1192     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1193     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



1194     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1195   */



1196  /* Prelookup - Index and Fraction



1197     Index Search method: 'binary'



1198     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



1199     Use previous index: 'off'



1200     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1201     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



1202     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1203   */



1204  if (u0 <= bp0[0U]) {



1205    iLeft = 0U;



1206    frac = 0ULL;



1207  } else if (u0 < bp0[maxIndex]) {



1208    /* Binary Search */



1209    bpIdx = maxIndex >> 1U;



1210    iLeft = 0U;



1211    iRght = maxIndex;



1212    while (iRght - iLeft > 1U) {



1213      if (u0 < bp0[bpIdx]) {



1214        iRght = bpIdx;



1215      } else {



1216        iLeft = bpIdx;



1217      }



1218



1219      bpIdx = (iRght + iLeft) >> 1U;



1220    }



1221



1222    frac = ((uint64_T)(uint16_T)((uint32_T)u0 - bp0[iLeft]) << 48) / (uint16_T)



1223      ((uint32_T)bp0[iLeft + 1U] - bp0[iLeft]);



1224  } else {



1225    iLeft = maxIndex - 1U;



1226    frac = 281474976710656ULL;



1227  }



1228



1229  /* Interpolation 1-D



1230     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



1231     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1232     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1233     Overflow mode: 'wrapping'



1234   */



1235  if (table[iLeft + 1U] >= table[iLeft]) {



1236    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)(uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft + 1U]



1237      - table[iLeft]) * frac) >> 48) + table[iLeft]);



1238  } else {



1239    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft] - (uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)



1240      table[iLeft] - table[iLeft + 1U]) * frac) >> 48));



1241  }



1242



1243  return y;



1244}
